(109, 1, '2022-09-06 13:16:43', '2022-09-06 13:16:43', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>By building temples in fishing villages, for spiritual awareness in the villages, so far 378 fishermen have been trained as priests and organized to perform pujas in our villages.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tirumala Tirupati Vari Ratha Yatra and Srinivasa Kalyanam are being held. Sri Matsyanarayana Swamy Temple has been constructed on the beach of Narasapuram in West Godavari district with crores of rupees.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Apart from that, Tirumala Tirupati Devasthanam has given idols of Lord Venkateswara and built temples in the state.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"linkTo\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":107,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://mssap.in/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Screenshot-from-2022-09-06-18-40-47.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-107\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":105,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://mssap.in/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Screenshot-from-2022-09-06-18-40-58.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-105\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":103,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://mssap.in/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Screenshot-from-2022-09-06-18-41-28.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-103\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":104,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://mssap.in/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Screenshot-from-2022-09-06-18-42-08.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-104\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:ima